project: Where is this..? Am I at the hospital?
Where is this..? Am I at the hospital?
No...It looks too fancy to be a hospital..
I must get out of here!
Huh? Who is this kid- is that me?!
Huh? Young Master, could it be that you've forgotten who I am?
Yes..I really don't know who you are, sorry
Oh no don't apologise! It's fine, the doctor warned us that there was a chance of memory loss due to the severity of your fever so don't worry about not remembering a few things
Please feel free to ask me any questions that you may have!
Young Master, you are Stella Nyx, the son of Duke and Duchess Nyx, and the heir to the Nyx dukedom
Stella Nyx...Nyx? Sounds familiar...Huh? Wait it can't be..!
(Novel...I'm in the world of the novel 'Isabella the divine maiden'?! ...And I'm the main villain..?!)
Young Master, you are in your bedroom. Ah that's too vague! To be more specific, Young Master is currently resting in the Nyx mansion in the capital.

Young Master...was poisoned and you were bedridden with a severe fever for a whole week! Rest assured the culprits have been caught and punished! Hmph, we will protect the Young Master! The Young Master is the precious heir to the Nyx Dukedom.
